square.name: Perfect Square
square.description: A product of some integer k squared.

prime.name: Prime
prime.description: Has no divisor other than itself and 1.

zeisel.name: Zeisel
zeisel.description: A square free number that has at least three prime factors of the form px = apx-1 + b.

triangular.name: Triangular
triangular.description: TODO Can form an equilateral triangle in cannon ball formation.

pentagonal.name: Pentagonal
pentagonal.description: A number that can form pentagonal shapes when evenly spaced.

hexagonal.name: Hexagonal
hexagonal.description: A number that form hexagonal shapes when evenly spaced.

mersenne.name: Mersenne
mersenne.description: A positive prime that is one less than the power of 2.

catalan.name: Catalan
catalan.description: Number of ways to insert n pairs of parentheses in a word of n+1 letters.

ramanujan.name: Hardy-Ramanujan
ramanujan.description: The smallest number expressible as the sum of two cubes in two different ways (1729=1<sup>3</sup>+12<sup>3</sup>=9<sup>3</sup>+10<sup>3</sup>).

taxicab.name: Taxicab
taxicab.description: The smallest number that can be expressed as a sum of two cubes in n ways.

cabtaxi.name: Cabtaxi
cabtaxi.description: The smallest positive integer that can be written as the sum of two positive or negative or 0 cubes in n ways.

sphenic.name: Sphenic
sphenic.description: The product of three distinct prime numbers.

triangularSquare.name: Triangular Square
triangularSquare.description: Both triangular and a perfect square.

automorphic.name: Automorphic
automorphic.description: It's square "ends" in itself. Also called Curious.

palindrome.name: Palindrome
palindrome.description: Reads the same forward and backward

factorial.name: Factorial
factorial.description: The product of all integers less than or equal - n!.
